Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:57.57,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you from my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:03.17,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you forever with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:21.66,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}每日从早到晚 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:26.22,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这样的生活不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:29.31,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一觉醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:31.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你已泡好热咖啡等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.40,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧紧抱住你的左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:41.49,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}以前曾屈指等待你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:46.58,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如今见到你的时间是越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:50.89,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)\be1}这样的幸福谁曾料到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:56.50,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,200)\be1}你和我 都堕入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:01.42,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:04.80,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}初次体会到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:08.95,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Oh 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.68,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:16.54,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此情不变
