Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年名叫橘纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁 高二生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体验了惨痛的失恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于心中这个旧伤 对恋爱甚为胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他本来就不是敢于主动出击的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是懦夫好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进一步说 是以失恋为借口而…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 能不能到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这位少年就是本作的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好有料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年和少女命运的邂逅…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假结束 第二学期到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过暑假洗礼 发生诸多事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校内冒出了一对又一对情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天在学校食堂吃夏季限定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华满腹定食 增强体力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增强多余的体力干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的爷们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为紧要关头做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥们 一起来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了 我没这必要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的暑假 十分遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连事件本身都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的物理作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后要收 记得交哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 讲义已经发给你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 说来还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石垣老师可是很恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 期限是到放学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那第五堂课就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课不准干别的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休报废了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭都没得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法 帮你买点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 心灵之友 此恩难忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我要猪扒三文治 可乐饼包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有冷面三文治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冒失鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐角处要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女觉得钱包「好…好可爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假旅行那时 我给你买了礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？全家一起去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}（呃…钱包…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物下次给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 少女的声音没能传到少年耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为少年脑海中浮现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死党饿着肚子等待的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得争分夺秒 买到面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回到他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 快奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原相信着你 等着你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 猪扒三文治 可乐饼包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷面三文治卖光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些给梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赶紧买乌冬吃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…貌似会很费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也买面包好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 钱包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 刚才还在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我的钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你捡到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在楼梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在楼梯撞到人时掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是少了这个鳕鱼子钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我午饭就吃不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 鳕鱼子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳕鱼子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这女生是前段时间那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你之前是穿其他学校的校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是插班生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我校午饭争夺战愈发激烈了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍晚一步 就成这鬼样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个白面包 要咱哥俩分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要去找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没向人家道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我全吃了行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了美也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级有没有像这样扎两束头发的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…是指双马尾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 还有 稍微有点弱势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像小动物一样的可爱女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有双水汪汪的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个子虽小 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该凸的地方凸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那女生怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才她帮我捡了这鳕鱼子钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好好跟她道个谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 在学校食堂买到午饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是中多纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个有点好色的人嘛 是我哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…美也 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 「该凸的地方凸」～像色猴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也能理解哥哥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫纱江身材惹火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时也会为了沾光而去摸她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摸她？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害～软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够…够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么软 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你色相又暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 虽然我哥这副德性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也请多关照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前见到你还是穿其他学校的校服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江是第二学期开学才转过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身校服也是刚刚才做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才捡到钱包还我 真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然间就跑开了 找得我好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江怕生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这钱包 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能道个谢 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次才是少年和少女货真价实的命运邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘…橘学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好害怕 不敢过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门后面 有条没拴上绳的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会不会越门而来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有门挡着应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来当护花使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的话应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也顺利通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 连那种小狗都怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问要点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你这算什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是你女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真见外 用不着隐瞒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 介绍一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是美也的同班同学 中多纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是我女朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫棚町薰 是纯一的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟薰从初中就开始打交道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没问到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还没下单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～最适合囊中羞涩之人 可无限续杯的咖啡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也要一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 两杯咖啡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们慢慢～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你好像很热心地在观察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服…好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这个有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想穿一次试试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没打过工么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 之前念的学校是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 我都没打过工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校允许打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以试试哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 可以问问薰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这里招不招兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您点的已经上齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡可以无限续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管吩咐就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 两位请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店现在招不招兼职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 常年招募中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想打工么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告诉她招工的详情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一小时就下班了 过后没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那等会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想试试打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先听她介绍一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰一定能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙虽然笨 不过很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天突然有人请假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还得换班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 没法跟你介绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 这家店招工会有个简单的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是面试啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点是考你能不能顺利跟客人沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及会不会上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上菜应该是没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟客人沟通就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年根本就没想过要做什么练习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时少女也无从得知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？于是就决定在我家练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥突然间带纱江过来 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得纱江想挑战兼职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我啊…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当教官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当教官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 叫声听听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教…教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 既然决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会严格指导你的 做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:16:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟美也说的一样 中多相当怕生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不下猛药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计过不了兼职测试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要加油特训 目标是通过测试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 能加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想努力…试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是让客人清楚听见你声音的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个朋友 家里是开寿司店的 叫梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他下店帮忙的时候 他爸是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「欢迎光临！」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是讲话要有威势 须从丹田发声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从丹田发声么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以为了能发出响声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先练习用腹部吸气吐气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训特训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吸气 鼓起肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吐气 让肚子瘪下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没鼓起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不只是吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还必须得吐气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下来是上菜的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 把咖啡端到我这里试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫好烫烫死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥这变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映入妹妹眼帘的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在自己好朋友面前脱裤的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 都是哥哥不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你做些让人误会的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个像学长…教官这样的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要的话随时拿去 我不会心疼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 好久没玩猜拳背人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你不是来真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳背人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 输家要背赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举例来说 布赢的话 就要说布丁菠萝派
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石赢的话 就说什锦烤菜之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按字数背着走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好玩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按赢家所指定词的字数走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及说过一次的词不能再用 规则是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩吧玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 看我教训一下你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石剪布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石剪布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢啦 哥哥输了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 哥哥输了 要背纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我就…免了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 愿赌服输非背不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 鼓足干劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我不会输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年此时想 永远输下去也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是想永远输下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 完全不重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 该 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「时人皆说巨乳好」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 丹田发声 来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时人皆说巨乳好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大声点 时人皆说巨乳好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时人皆说巨乳好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出自少女之口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本只是稍带点黄的词语 变得相当黄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传到了少年耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很响亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时～人～皆～说～巨～乳～好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚霞中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背人的少年和被人背的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这夏季将过 秋季将至之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩命运的齿轮是否开始转动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此 他们自己都还不知道
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 你色相毕露哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟身材劲爆的学妹玩猜拳背人输了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还觉得「赚翻了赚翻了」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:23:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 特训
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟中多特训的日子还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也和中多的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲逢哦 学长
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM-----------------------------------
